data.description: This centrally located Lewiston Orchards home is ready for your finishing touches to make it your own. 4 bedroom with possible 5th, 2 1/2 bath, one level with basement and attached 2 car garage. Updated kitchen with luxury vinyl flooring. Large family room with extra room for craft room or office. Newer roof and windows with fenced front and back yard. Close to schools and shopping.
